"{\"uid\": \"newzimbabwe.com-paris-2024-olympics-letsile-tebogo-claims-200m-gold-as-noah-lyles-takes-bronze\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Date:  Tebogo, 21, stormed clear of his rivals to clock an African record of 19.46 seconds and finish ahead of American Kenneth Bednarek, who crossed the line in 19.62.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 111, \"end\": 119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.99993735309834, \"rank\": 3.9367018378157006e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 120, \"end\": 136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenneth Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles, crowned the world's fastest man by five-thousandths of a second in ahistorically quick 100m finalon Sunday night, was unable to compete at the head of the race and matched his Tokyo bronze in 19.70.\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9950047150149114, \"rank\": 0.005020332544223617, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It emerged after the race that Lyles had tested positive for Covid and the 27-year-old had to be helped off the track in a wheelchair.\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9501344707235196, \"rank\": 0.05248038970122696, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having burst out on to the track to huge cheers before the race, Lyles was seeking to become the first man since Usain Bolt in 2016 to complete a 100m and 200m double at an Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9501344707235196, \"rank\": 0.05248038970122696, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 626, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Usain_Bolt\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Tebogo had other ideas.\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A world bronze medallist over the distance last year, Tebogo also took 100m silver in Budapest as Lyles completed a golden treble.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 861, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.7756860137398781, \"rank\": 0.2891814242298678, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9501344707235196, \"rank\": 0.05248038970122696, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a dazzling return for Tebogo at his first senior global championship, but it was nothing compared to his achievement at the Stade de France as he marked his first Olympics with a gold.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tebogo, sixth in the Paris 100m final, lined up with a 200m personal best of 19.50 - notably down on the favourite's 19.31.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998112798, \"rank\": 1.8875121637907312e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Showman Lyles made his entrance to huge excitement, seemingly ready to seize his moment with the eyes of the world fixed upon him, but he remained third throughout following a slow start.\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9501344707235196, \"rank\": 0.05248038970122696, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bednarek held out to equal his silver of three years ago in Tokyo - a medal he also won at the 2022 World Championships - but could not overhaul Tebogo, who sprinted clear to win Botswana's first ever Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9950047150149114, \"rank\": 0.005020332544223617, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbped